Hardware Requirements

Minimum (Recommended for smooth usage):
	•	64-bit x86 CPU (Intel Skylake or newer recommended)
	•	4 GB RAM (8 GB recommended for better multitasking)
	•	20 GB storage
	•	UEFI firmware (Legacy supported but not guaranteed)

## GPU Compatibility

Current validation status for StellaOS Dev 1.1:

- Intel integrated graphics: fully tested and recommended
- AMD graphics: not officially tested
- NVIDIA graphics: not officially tested

StellaOS Dev 1.1 is primarily validated on Intel integrated graphics systems.  
Compatibility with other GPUs may vary and could require additional configuration.